    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Fighter Cunning Edge</strong><br/><br/><p>As a full round action that provokes an attack of opportunity, the opportunist can combine two alchemical weapons into a single vial. When thrown as a splash weapon, the mixture has the effects of both component substances and targets are affected as if hit by both. The mixture becomes inert after 1 hour. Combining identical alchemical weapons has no effect. The opportunist can use this ability once per day for every 4 fighter levels he has.</p>",
